###########################################
## ErpApp Widget Generator             ####
## Version 1.0                         ####
###########################################

script/generate erp_app_widget [widget_name] [description] [icon_url] (optional fields) [plugin to create in]

What has been created

1. Folder structure [plugin]/lib/widgets/[widget_name]

2. javascript folder with default widget setup

3. views folder with index.html.erb

4. ErpApp::Widgets::[widget_name]::Base class that extends from ErpApp::Widgets::Base